con:configuration.script:
def productSpecCharId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char#res_productSpecCharId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charId", productSpecCharId.toString());

def productSpecCharExtId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char#res_productSpecCharExtId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charExtId", productSpecCharExtId);

def productSpecCharValueId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char value#res_productSpecCharValueId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charValueId", productSpecCharValueId);

def productSpecCharValueExtId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char value#res_productSpecCharValueExtId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charValueExtId", productSpecCharValueExtId);

def productSpecCharUseId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char use#res_productSpecCharUseId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charUseId", productSpecCharUseId);

def productSpecCharUseExtId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char use#res_productSpecCharUseExtId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charUseExtId", productSpecCharUseExtId);

def productSpecCharValueUseId = context.expand( '${Create product spec char value use#res_productSpecCharValueUseId}' )
testRunner.testCase.testSteps['Properties'].setPropertyValue("charValueUseId", productSpecCharValueUseId);
